I'm twenty nine, no kids, never married I like to play sports, listen to music, read etc. . . Despite how I write I'm a really silly guy and don't try to take too many things too seriously because of this, plus life's short. I live in California, but that doesn't mean the woman for me has to be here as well. I don't think the woman for me has to be within a thirty-mile radius and it's pretty narrow-minded to think so. I'm looking for a woman who is willing to visit California, I understand not everyone would be and that's find just disregard this whole ad if this isn't you. If it is then keep reading. As far as the kind of women I like I like sweet women who have an innocent side but also a freaky one when need be, someone clean of course, faithful, loyal and not a liar. I'm not into married women or women who are still living with their ex or who sleep around a lot. Physically I like a big thick woman who has very large/'huge breast over D D D a lot of women think they do, (or try to give the illusion they do by standing sideways), but I've noticed they don't, at least not to my standard. I'm half black and Italian;

I tend not to care about race too much though. Also I can't cook so if I do find a special girl who wants to visit, if you can't cook then T.V dinners is what's on the menu, yummy.

Well if interested, please message me and send a full picture, I won't respond without one simply because I'll assume its spam and PLEASE PLEASE no gay guys. I'm not gay, I'm not bi, never have been never will be, please get it through your head, I only like women, it's a shame all these beautiful women are running out of a selection of straight guys these days.

Fifty-Something Man with Empty Boat Seeks Lady Companion to Make Boat Less Empty. Looking for a Lady with a very very sweet personality. PLEASE INCLUDE A RECENT PHOTO IN YOUR EMAIL, IF YOU WANT ME TO REPLY.

MARRIAGE MINDED LADIES ONLY REPLY- if you are just after a good time, after a drinking buddy, a text buddy, a pen pal, or just someone to tell your friends about please look elsewhere and move on. I don't have time to waste. I am looking for someone that has a goal of getting married one day as well. Life is too short and time is too precious.

Romantic, IT Professional, self-motivated, fun, sweet disposition, cool, funny, boat, own house, Italian, great cook, artist. I am for real and very single. 

First off, I'm 53, male, very fit, and a little obsessed with biking due to the stunning scenery on the coast of Florida's beaches. I'm also a Professional with a crazy schedule and have a nice place near St. Augustine. Sounds pretty good, right? Wrong. So wrong. I've got a huge problem. You see, I've got this fabulous life and, well, there's no one else in it to share. Big problem. Not okay. What I need is a co-captain in my life. 

Co-captain requirement include-
must be over 33; MUST BE EMPLOYED, HAVE own transportation and place to live- NO DRAMA PLEASE!! NO SUGAR DADDY SEEKERS!

not required to laugh at bad jokes, but must have a high tolerance for them; 
must love BBQ, as it is the only thing I can cook; 
a sharp wit is priority; 
physical dimensions are important; 
must possess hopelessly romantic tendencies; 
must be patient with an IT geek's unpredictable schedule; 
must have brilliant, beautiful, strong mind of her own. 

I love science fiction, hiking, and Italy...not necessarily all together or in that particular order. I've heard my back rubs are as lousy as my memory, so maybe you can help me improve on one or both of those. I love a beautiful woman with a goofy laugh as much as I love a goofy-looking woman with a beautiful laugh. I dance better than I sing, but I sing better than I play sports. 

I want my lover to be my best friend, my confidante, my rock, and, most importantly, someone to help me with my cufflinks (those things are impossible). 


Cheers to you. 

Tony

